  "pages": [
    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The Northern Pacific is rushing\nwith all possible speed the work OF\ndouble-tracking between Spokane\nand Wins, five miles west. The\ncost of the work will be about\nS250,00O. The work is expected to\nbe finished by the latter part OF\nthe month and the Northern Pacific\nwill then have double track from\nSpokane to Marshall Junction,\nwhich will add materially to the\nservice and safety of the road."
    }
